{"tid":1166114,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"微軟網店下架華為手提電腦!!","createTime":"2019-05-22T08:29:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T09:01:40.000Z","uid":83518,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9007d4773229dcd550bcedf727b1392422b5d229","tid":1166114,"uid":83518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"繼美國商務部將華為及旗下68家附屬事業，列入有貿易黑名單 後，Google 決定停止授權 Android 系統與 Google 服務給華為。最新一間科技企業微軟（Microsoft）也有跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n據《Business Insider》報道，雖然有現貨可以供應，但微軟上周末從網上商店中刪除了華為手提電腦Matebook，也引發該公司是否計劃阻止華為手提電腦的Windows 10更新的疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n由於華為的所有手提電腦都在Windows操作系統上運作，因此若微軟不再將其軟體和其他產品授權給華為，可能嚴重影響華為的手提電腦業務。<br />\n<br />\n另外微軟可能是因為安全漏洞而有此舉措。今年1月美國微軟在華為手提電腦發現一項安全性漏洞，研究人員在華為Matebook手提電腦發現後門。但當時微軟向華為回報此缺陷後，華為已迅速對軟件進行修補。<br />\n<br />\n微軟目前尚未就其與華為的關係發表官方聲明，但也不願意證實微軟將阻止華為手提電腦的Windows 10更新，僅簡短表示「我們沒有什麼可分享的」。<br />\n<br />\n由於禁令緣故，英特爾（Intel）、高通（Qualcomm）、博通（Broadcom）和賽靈思（Xilinx）等美國晶片製造商已告知員工，將停止向華為供貨。至於微軟是否成為下一家圍堵華為的廠商，仍有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1505821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1505821%2F&d=cCjVArjaL4JVgeQxTlbTS1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=17c15f88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1505821%2F&h=29d6461a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1505821/</a>"},{"pid":"0ea43190d2d97a4c98978a2acdb54246efa17125","tid":1166114,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:31:33.000Z","msg":"冇所謂啦，啲打手話鎖國都夠食喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fef93f0360046cc436b929ee74181093d846fd88","tid":1166114,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:38:24.000Z","msg":"華為話自己唔怕架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人真係嘴炮最有一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c0d578d01d9238aed9f3ebde47903e37fe37b35","tid":1166114,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"人地用行動証明, 華為就用嘴炮抵抗"},{"pid":"8ac8572e2e87ae9c7083f6c61c626395282295eb","tid":1166114,"uid":83518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1c0d578d01d9238aed9f3ebde47903e37fe37b35","tid":1166114,"uid":13914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"人地用行動証明, 華為就用嘴炮抵抗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"繼續死頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}